Grub entries & BIOS boot order
------------------------------

Be aware that changing the BBS (?) order of hard drive is changing the
apparent mapping of partitions. Thus `hd0` and `hd1` are inverted. I
assume that this is also true for devices like /dev/sda and /dev/sdb.

